abstract: >-
  An anonymized, reproducible research snapshot testing whether base language
  models can self-detect unsupported title-artist relations in open-ended music
  recommendation, with counterfactual and causal mechanism diagnostics.
keywords:
  - mechanistic interpretability
  - music recommendation
  - hallucination
